General.Name: Rumble Resources Ltd
General.Description: Rumble Resources Limited engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of base and precious metal projects in Australia. The company explores for zinc, lead, copper, silver, nickel, cobalt, lithium, tantalum, niobium, tin, and gold deposits. The company's flagship project is the Earaheedy project located in Western Australia. Rumble Resources Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
